<section id="honorific">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>titles</primary>

      <secondary>creating new</secondary>
    </indexterm>Title</title>

  <para>To create a new Title, select the NEW button. The following screen
  will appear:</para>

  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/honorific.png"/>
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Create New Title</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>

  <para>When creating a new Title, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Title</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the Title here (e.g., Dr., Mr., Ms., etc.).</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
